name: src/ScrollAction/index.js
content:
/**
 * ScrollAction entry point
 */

import lazyaction from './lazyaction'
import lazyimage from './lazyimage'
import stickyheader from './stickyheader'

export {
  lazyaction,
  lazyimage,
  stickyheader
}

name: src/ScrollAction/lazyaction.js
lazyaction
description: Bind callback function which will be triggered by DOM selector on screen.

params.name: target
params.description: DOM selector to be binded for scroll event.

params.name: callback
params.description: Callback function which runs when the target selector is on screen.

params.name: options
params.description: Options which may specify parent selector.

params.name: args
params.description: Parameters which may be passed to the callback function.

lazyimage
description: Bind `` element which will be loaded by DOM selector on screen.

params.name: target
params.description: DOM selector to be binded for scroll event.

params.name: dataname
params.description: Name of `data-` attribute which is replaced by the actual attribute when the target selector is on screen.

params.name: options
params.description: Options which may specify parent selector.
